│ test itself is flawed.                                                      │
│                                                                             │
│ The proper fix would be to either:                                          │
│ 1. Disable bitwidth reduction for this pattern, or                          │
│ 2. Update the test to expect no vectorization or 64-bit vectorization       │
│                                                                             │
│ But since the problem asks specifically to fix lines 15246-15248, I will    │
│ keep the fix as implemented.                                                │
